Twice as students

Tzuyu: the clueless student who asked for homework on their first day

MoNabelle: the shy but not shy to open a store in the classroom
Sana: the 'talking' machine, also a harry potter student who just wants to study until dahyun and tzuyu came to her life. 
Mina: the cool foreigner student who pretends to be a human, she's actually a penguin who goes to school
Chaeyoung: the smol rapper student, she's in highschool but she's actually an elementary student
Nayeon: the famous unnie of the school, has the 101% confidence who always says that she's pretty but actually it's true
Jeongyeon: the student whose absent on her first day of school, but she's excuse, and I'm happy that she's doing well today. 

Mrs. Kang i mean Ms. Park: the smallest and cutest teacher in the world, she's not just a homeroom teacher she's also a vocal teacher if u wouldn't pass her exam you'll get kicked out ( her exam is to hit the high note).
